  "text": "is multilevel dynamics has been used to study the animal behavior [CITATION_1] , formation of epileptic seizures [CITATION_2] , and the sustained levels of wakefulness in humans [CITATION_3] . is is a brief review of the concepts of EEG phase cones and their possible applications to brain behavior and epilepsy localization.",
